WeeWM - Installation instructions
=================================

1) Run 'make'

2) As root : run 'make install'

3) Modify your .xinitrc to run WeeWM at Xfree startup
   
   At first startup, WeeWM will automatically create
   default config files :
     ~/.weewm/config.rc
     ~/.weewm/keys.rc
   You can customize these files.

4) Enjoy !  :-)
